column4: Apple files $1 billion lawsuit against chip supplier Qualcomm
column5: Apple Inc filed a $1 billion lawsuit against supplier Qualcomm Inc on Friday  days after the U.S. government accused the chip maker of resorting to anticompetitive tactics to maintain a monopoly over key semiconductors in mobile phones.
